The Top Performers 

Want to see where your players rank among the top scorers in your Fantasy league? Click Statistics, Player Scoring on the toolbar. Initially, you'll see a list of your players, in order of the top Fantasy point scorers this season. Choose All Teams and All Positions from the listboxes above the report to view every player in the league, ranked by Fantasy points, and see how your players stack up. 

