Audibles 

Are you searching for that key free agent to propel your team into playoff contention, or to solidify your team's position atop the standings? Let us help. Read Audibles every Wednesday in our Fantasy News area (click News, Fantasy News on the toolbar) for our recommended pickups and drops for the week. 

